ts_tbl(..., key, index = NULL, interval = hours(1L))

as_ts_tbl(tbl, key, index = NULL, interval = hours(1L))

Arguments

...

Passed to data.table::data.table()/generic compatibility.
object

A ts_tbl object.
row.names, optional

Generic consistency: passing anything other than the default value issues a warning.
key

Character or numeric vector of at least length 1, identifying columns that combined with time stamps, uniquely identify rows.
index

Character or numeric vector of length 1, identifying the column that defines temporal ordering.
interval

Scalar value, defining time steps between rows (assuming complete time series data).
tbl

An object inheriting from data.frame.
